show.title: The Natural Nurse

title: The Natural Nurse
content:
Host. Dr. Eugene Zampieron, MD, MH, www.drznaturally.com,  interviews Victoria Maizes MD. Dr. <!--more--> Maizes is the executive director of the University of Arizona Center for Integrative Medicine and a Professor of Medicine and Public Health.
Her newest book Be Fruitful: The Essential Guide to Maximizing Fertility and Giving Birth to a Healthy Child offers an integrative and hands-on approach to getting pregnant, having a happy and healthy pregnancy and delivering a healthy child and is now available on Amazon.
For more information visit her website victoriamaizesmd.
com or follow her on twitter @vmaizes.
